---
title: BBQ Chicken with Potato Wedges and Homemade Baked Beans
description: The classic combination of chicken and bacon works brilliantly in this delicious recipe created by our Head Chef, Andre. Chicken fillets are rubbed with BBQ sauce, wrapped in streaky bacon and baked until crispy and golden brown before being served up with homemade smokey baked beans and chunky potato wedges. A guaranteed crowd-pleaser.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bbq-chicken-040d51cc-4fab9941.jpg
